partman-basicfilesystems (54) unstable; urgency=low

  * Mount vfat filesystems with the utf8 mount option if the locale contains
    ".UTF-8" (closes: #413248).
  * Move sanity-checking scripts from finish.d to check.d. Requires
    partman-base 106.

