  * Turkish (tr.po) by Recai Oktaş
  * Ukrainian (uk.po) by Eugeniy Meshcheryakov
  * Wolof (wo.po) by Mouhamadou Mamoune Mbacke
  * Simplified Chinese (zh_CN.po) by Ming Hua

